:

1. *Gluposti* su sastavni deo ljudskog života. (Foolishness is an integral part of human life.)
2. Neću da slušam tvoje *gluposti*. (I won't listen to your foolishness.)
3. Dosta mi je tvojih *gluposti*. (I've had enough of your foolishness.)
4. *Gluposti* koje govoriš ne vrede ništa. (The foolishness you're talking about is worth nothing.)
5. Neću da slušam tvoje prazne *gluposti*. (I won't listen to your empty foolishness.)